{
	"modName": "PickmansWhisper",
	"displayName": "Pickman's Whisper",
	"minMcmVersion": 1,
	"plugin": "PickmansWhisper.esp",
	"content": [
		{
			"type": "spacer",
			"numLines": 2
		},
		{
			"text": "<p align='center'><font size='40'><b>Pickman's Whisper</b></font></p>",
			"type": "text",
			"html": true
		},
		{
			"text": "<p align='center'><font size='20'>Knife voice · serial hunger (not sexual)</font></p>",
			"type": "text",
			"html": true
		},
		{
			"text": "<p align='center'><font size='18'>Version 0.2.0 · Slice B</font></p>",
			"type": "text",
			"html": true
		},
		{
			"type": "spacer",
			"numLines": 1
		},
		{
			"text": "<p align='center'>Companion to <b>Necromantic</b>. Open <b>Debug</b> to verify F4SE / forms.</p>",
			"type": "text",
			"html": true
		}
	],
	"pages": [
		{
			"pageDisplayName": "How To Use",
			"content": [
				{
					"text": "Hook",
					"type": "section"
				},
				{
					"text": "Enter <b>Pickman Gallery</b> (interior) or obtain / equip <b>Pickman's Blade</b>. A voice bonds with the wielder — toast-only for Slice A.",
					"type": "text",
					"html": true
				},
				{
					"text": "Hunger",
					"type": "section"
				},
				{
					"text": "Once bonded, hunger rises with unused knife-time. High hunger applies <b>Knife Hunger</b> withdrawal (AGI/CHA −1). Kill a non-essential human with <b>Pickman's Blade</b> to sate hunger (praise toast + sated window).",
					"type": "text",
					"html": true
				},
				{
					"text": "Butcher menu",
					"type": "section"
				},
				{
					"text": "With <b>Pickman's Blade</b> drawn, aim at a dead adult woman and press <b>/</b> to open the <b>butcher menu</b>. Choose a limb — same combat gore (piece stays visible). Skipped during Necromantic scenes.",
					"type": "text",
					"html": true
				},
				{
					"text": "Bed gift",
					"type": "section"
				},
				{
					"text": "After the bond, sometimes a corpse appears in your bed when you sleep. Look away and she is gone. Toggle under <b>Voice</b>.",
					"type": "text",
					"html": true
				},
				{
					"text": "Suite",
					"type": "section"
				},
				{
					"text": "Soft load order: Occult Pact → Pickman's Whisper → Necromantic. This mod is <b>not sexual</b>; Necromantic handles corpse scenes afterward.",
					"type": "text",
					"html": true
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"pageDisplayName": "Hunger",
			"content": [
				{
					"text": "Status",
					"type": "section"
				},
				{
					"id": "sBondState:Hunger",
					"text": "Bond",
					"type": "textinput",
					"valueOptions": {
						"sourceType": "ModSettingString"
					}
				},
				{
					"id": "sHungerLevel:Hunger",
					"text": "Current hunger",
					"type": "textinput",
					"valueOptions": {
						"sourceType": "ModSettingString"
					}
				},
				{
					"id": "sHungerSated:Hunger",
					"text": "Sated",
					"type": "textinput",
					"valueOptions": {
						"sourceType": "ModSettingString"
					}
				},
				{
					"text": "Show hunger info",
					"type": "button",
					"action": {
						"type": "CallFunction",
						"form": "PickmansWhisper.esp|800",
						"function": "ShowHungerInfo",
						"scriptName": "PickmansWhisperMainQuestScript"
					}
				},
				{
					"text": "Test: push hunger to addicted",
					"type": "button",
					"action": {
						"type": "CallFunction",
						"form": "PickmansWhisper.esp|800",
						"function": "ForceHungerAddictedTest",
						"scriptName": "PickmansWhisperMainQuestScript"
					}
				},
				{
					"text": "Test: satiate hunger (debug)",
					"type": "button",
					"help": "Clears hunger and plays a praise line without a real kill.",
					"action": {
						"type": "CallFunction",
						"form": "PickmansWhisper.esp|800",
						"function": "DebugSatiateHunger",
						"scriptName": "PickmansWhisperMainQuestScript"
					}
				},
				{
					"text": "System",
					"type": "section"
				},
				{
					"id": "bAddictionSpell:Hunger",
					"text": "Knife Hunger effect",
					"type": "switcher",
					"help": "When hunger is high, apply AGI/CHA withdrawal stand-in.",
					"valueOptions": {
						"sourceType": "ModSettingBool"
					}
				},
				{
					"text": "Rates",
					"type": "section"
				},
				{
					"id": "fTimeGain:Hunger",
					"text": "Hunger per game-hour",
					"type": "slider",
					"help": "Idle growth while bonded and not sated. Default 5.",
					"valueOptions": {
						"min": 0,
						"max": 15,
						"step": 0.5,
						"sourceType": "ModSettingFloat"
					}
				},
				{
					"id": "fAddictedAt:Hunger",
					"text": "Addicted threshold",
					"type": "slider",
					"valueOptions": {
						"min": 25,
						"max": 100,
						"step": 5,
						"sourceType": "ModSettingFloat"
					}
				},
				{
					"id": "fSatedHours:Hunger",
					"text": "Sated duration (game hours)",
					"type": "slider",
					"help": "After satiation (Slice B knife kill / debug button).",
					"valueOptions": {
						"min": 0.5,
						"max": 48,
						"step": 0.5,
						"sourceType": "ModSettingFloat"
					}
				}
			]
		},
		{
